article_title: GOP Debate Reveals The Outsiders Are Out Of Policy Ideas

article_metadata.description: Many people view the rise of the outsiders as a victory – out with the old, in with the new. But last night’s debate revealed how little thought the outsiders have given to actually governing. This should concern voters.
article_metadata.author: Abby McCloskey
